Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.25,0:06:58.88,Default,,0,0,0,,真绪
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.39,0:07:09.38,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么啊 金刚寺先生
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.04,0:07:12.79,Default,,0,0,0,,老爸
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.98,0:07:21.68,Default,,0,0,0,,打扰了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.04,0:07:25.58,Default,,0,0,0,,有报告说发现了可疑人物
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.85,0:07:26.32,Default,,0,0,0,,你说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.58,0:07:27.56,Default,,0,0,0,,是什么人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.09,0:07:28.80,Default,,0,0,0,,关于这点…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.06,0:07:31.43,Default,,0,0,0,,据…据说骑着白马
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.79,0:07:36.09,Default,,0,0,0,,真绪在哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.18,0:07:41.94,Default,,0,0,0,,真绪在哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.97,0:07:46.44,Default,,0,0,0,,大小姐她啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.94,0:07:49.74,Default,,0,0,0,,马上要到国外去了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.97,0:08:06.57,Default,,0,0,0,,去吧 叶太郎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.56,0:08:11.45,Default,,0,0,0,,如果这次你的信念是百折不饶的的话
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.02,0:08:12.90,Default,,0,0,0,,那就继续前进吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.38,0:08:19.14,Default,,0,0,0,,等…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.14,0:08:19.86,Default,,0,0,0,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.64,0:08:26.28,Default,,0,0,0,,大婶 要是你碍我好事的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.23,0:08:29.27,Default,,0,0,0,,铠太娇惯孩子了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.56,0:08:46.93,Default,,0,0,0,,骑…骑士枪
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.63,0:08:50.20,Default,,0,0,0,,难道你也是骑士吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.74,0:08:52.41,Default,,0,0,0,,我只是一介女仆
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.84,0:08:54.15,Default,,0,0,0,,所以这是…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.90,0:08:58.08,Default,,0,0,0,,惩罚
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.31,0:09:02.01,Default,,0,0,0,,真绪
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.58,0:09:05.56,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢你 长枪骑士
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.58,0:09:05.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs30\pos(694,665)}Knight Lancer
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.72,0:09:13.31,Default,,0,0,0,,你来救我 给我勇气 给我希望
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.68,0:09:15.08,Default,,0,0,0,,真是谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.89,0:09:18.58,Default,,0,0,0,,我是第一次遇到真正的英雄
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.84,0:09:22.20,Default,,0,0,0,,长枪骑士是真正的英雄
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.84,0:09:22.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs30\pos(540,665)}Knight Lancer
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.37,0:09:27.32,Default,,0,0,0,,我也想成为像你那样的真正的英雄
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.08,0:09:40.68,Default,,0,0,0,,叶太郎比长枪骑士差太远 太没用了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.08,0:09:40.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs30\pos(588,665)}Knight Lancer
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.19,0:09:45.22,Default,,0,0,0,,我在叶太郎饥饿难忍的时候 下了决心去救他
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.63,0:09:47.56,Default,,0,0,0,,如果换做是长枪骑士 也会这样做吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.63,0:09:47.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs30\pos(614,665)}Knight Lancer
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.51,0:09:50.16,Default,,0,0,0,,在我救了叶太郎之后
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.48,0:09:54.37,Default,,0,0,0,,爱丽丝和白姬还有依子也和我一起生活了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.95,0:09:56.82,Default,,0,0,0,,我真是太开心了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.29,0:10:00.08,Default,,0,0,0,,我想 这一切都是多亏了长枪骑士
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.29,0:10:00.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs30\pos(812,665)}Knight Lancer
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.53,0:10:01.33,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.11,0:10:05.69,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢你 长枪骑士
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.11,0:10:05.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs30\pos(694,665)}Knight Lancer
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.42,0:10:09.43,Default,,0,0,0,,真绪
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.13,0:10:34.13,Default,,0,0,0,,叶太郎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.86,0:10:36.53,Default,,0,0,0,,我一直都很胆小
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.59,0:10:38.68,Default,,0,0,0,,总是一味地逃避
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.31,0:10:42.88,Default,,0,0,0,,就算知道了真绪小姐的情况 也是束手无策
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.37,0:10:46.04,Default,,0,0,0,,不对 是我视而不见了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.78,0:10:51.40,Default,,0,0,0,,而且 明明已经发过誓不会再和犯罪扯上关系了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.34,0:10:54.58,Default,,0,0,0,,可是还是放不下这个
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.05,0:11:01.40,Default,,0,0,0,,叶太郎 我来指引你
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.25,0:11:18.24,Default,,0,0,0,,金刚寺先生
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.05,0:11:37.54,Default,,0,0,0,,请你让开 金刚寺先生
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.94,0:11:41.14,Default,,0,0,0,,我一定要到真绪的身边去
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.74,0:11:46.90,Default,,0,0,0,,真绪的愿望 真绪的想法
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.56,0:11:50.78,Default,,0,0,0,,我希望她能永远都充满笑容
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.43,0:11:56.08,Default,,0,0,0,,金刚寺先生你 也是明白真绪真正的想法的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.39,0:11:59.42,Default,,0,0,0,,请你回答我 金刚寺先生
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.58,0:12:00.28,Default,,0,0,0,,少废话
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.17,0:12:04.88,Default,,0,0,0,,用行动来传达你的想法！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.79,0:12:17.44,Default,,0,0,0,,丽王
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.96,0:12:25.53,Default,,0,0,0,,不见了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.57,0:12:43.83,Default,,0,0,0,,长枪骑士
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.57,0:12:43.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs30\pos(640,665)}Knight Lancer
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.32,0:12:51.07,Default,,0,0,0,,我是…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.31,0:12:56.39,Default,,0,0,0,,长枪骑士
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.31,0:12:56.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs30\pos(640,665)}Knight Lancer
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.86,0:13:00.47,Default,,0,0,0,,丽王！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.56,0:13:14.52,Default,,0,0,0,,叶太郎 不 长枪骑士
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.56,0:13:14.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs30\pos(715.2,665)}Knight Lancer
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.03,0:13:18.06,Default,,0,0,0,,既然你要和我对抗到底的话
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.03,0:13:20.86,Default,,0,0,0,,我也唯有全力迎战了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.56,0:13:23.15,Default,,0,0,0,,毕竟这也是骑士的礼仪
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.56,0:13:40.54,Default,,0,0,0,,叶太郎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.23,0:13:53.88,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么会…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.62,0:14:00.27,Default,,0,0,0,,这是…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.11,0:14:02.79,Default,,0,0,0,,棺材
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.62,0:14:08.52,Default,,0,0,0,,你的父亲 被称为传说的骑士的男人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.76,0:14:12.34,Default,,0,0,0,,每次赶赴战场 必会带上一口棺材
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.21,0:14:18.67,Default,,0,0,0,,他做好了不是敌人 就是自己躺进去的觉悟
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.71,0:14:20.42,Default,,0,0,0,,觉悟…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.48,0:14:27.85,Default,,0,0,0,,先锋之枪
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.48,0:14:27.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs30\pos(640,665)}Rhon Gomyniad
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.25,0:14:30.88,Default,,0,0,0,,你想做什么 森
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.83,0:14:33.90,Default,,0,0,0,,先锋之枪只有你…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.83,0:14:33.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs30\pos(575.2,665)}Rhon Gomyniad
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.78,0:15:01.58,Default,,0,0,0,,这不可能
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.50,0:15:05.21,Default,,0,0,0,,不对
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.71,0:15:09.60,Default,,0,0,0,,白姬
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.63,0:15:22.66,Default,,0,0,0,,手握先锋之枪的骑士
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.63,0:15:22.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs30\pos(623.2,665)}Rhon Gomyniad
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.21,0:15:25.62,Default,,0,0,0,,那我也拿出全力与你一战吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.70,0:15:40.78,Default,,0,0,0,,长枪突击
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.70,0:15:40.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs30\pos(640,665)}Lance Charge
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.23,0:15:58.43,Default,,0,0,0,,当将自己的灵魂奉献给公主之时
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.86,0:16:03.28,Default,,0,0,0,,骑士会发挥语无论比的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.58,0:16:26.27,Default,,0,0,0,,父亲…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.37,0:16:40.99,Default,,0,0,0,,女士
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.57,0:16:49.78,Default,,0,0,0,,让你久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.53,0:16:54.23,Default,,0,0,0,,我向你发誓
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.79,0:16:59.49,Default,,0,0,0,,骑士绝不会违背心地善良的女士你的心意
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.55,0:17:04.16,Default,,0,0,0,,不论何时 不论你身处何地
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.67,0:17:07.97,Default,,0,0,0,,都会尽我一生守护你
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.33,0:17:25.32,Default,,0,0,0,,老爹 怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.72,0:17:27.04,Default,,0,0,0,,醒过来啊 老爹
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.81,0:17:31.48,Default,,0,0,0,,不可能 老爹是不会输给任何人的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.83,0:17:34.11,Default,,0,0,0,,老爹…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.87,0:17:38.52,Default,,0,0,0,,爸爸 快醒啊 爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.96,0:17:42.88,Default,,0,0,0,,还不快点起来 我又要去做坏事了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.32,0:17:45.14,Default,,0,0,0,,真的要去做不好的事情咯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.17,0:17:46.87,Default,,0,0,0,,给我让开
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.13,0:17:48.68,Default,,0,0,0,,快点
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.70,0:17:51.16,Default,,0,0,0,,不 不要
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.68,0:17:55.81,Default,,0,0,0,,不想你父亲死的话 就赶紧让开
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.39,0:18:07.27,Default,,0,0,0,,老爹！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.53,0:18:10.44,Default,,0,0,0,,依子
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.03,0:18:12.68,Default,,0,0,0,,好见不久 铠
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.70,0:18:18.21,Default,,0,0,0,,叶太郎他获得了先锋之枪
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.70,0:18:18.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs30\pos(757.2,665)}Rhon Gomyniad
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.18,0:18:24.58,Default,,0,0,0,,先锋之枪本是只有被选中的那一位骑士才能拥有
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.18,0:18:24.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs30\pos(359.2,665)}Rhon Gomyniad
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.24,0:18:27.80,Default,,0,0,0,,然而森应该是它现在的主人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.80,0:18:32.38,Default,,0,0,0,,但是 先锋之枪却对叶太郎做出了反应
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.80,0:18:32.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs30\pos(513.2,665)}Rhon Gomyniad
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.33,0:18:37.02,Default,,0,0,0,,依子 叶太郎他到底是什么人？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.87,0:18:54.09,Default,,0,0,0,,依子小姐 父亲他…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.01,0:19:09.88,Default,,0,0,0,,伊子小姐 我们回家吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.91,0:19:16.18,Default,,0,0,0,,是吗 我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.85,0:19:22.74,Default,,0,0,0,,骑士和公主邂逅了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.27,0:19:23.89,Default,,0,0,0,,森
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.88,0:19:26.74,Default,,0,0,0,,好久不见呢 明
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.27,0:19:30.72,Default,,0,0,0,,别插手真绪的事
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.85,0:19:35.56,Default,,0,0,0,,为那孩子的命运着想 就绝不要接近她
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.25,0:19:39.12,Default,,0,0,0,,但也不能一直将她封锁在孤塔里啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.67,0:19:42.48,Default,,0,0,0,,骑士为了守护公主 才会奋不顾身
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.95,0:19:45.69,Default,,0,0,0,,而公主也正因骑士的守护才能放出耀眼的光辉
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.00,0:19:48.05,Default,,0,0,0,,那才是那些孩子的命运
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.40,0:19:52.08,Default,,0,0,0,,这只是你自己的期望吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.35,0:19:58.62,Default,,0,0,0,,别把你没能保护好结真的悔恨 强加于真绪身上
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.65,0:20:03.61,Default,,0,0,0,,真绪是我和结真的女儿 这点你别忘了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.46,0:20:05.95,Default,,0,0,0,,那孩子是公主
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.83,0:20:10.29,Default,,0,0,0,,然后叶太郎 是骑士
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.18,0:20:13.74,Default,,0,0,0,,当潜藏在叶太郎身上的力量觉醒之时
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.13,0:20:16.66,Default,,0,0,0,,他就能成为真正的骑士了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.83,0:20:20.00,Default,,0,0,0,,这一次 一定能保护好公主的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.25,0:20:33.97,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么样？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.32,0:20:36.29,Default,,0,0,0,,很合身哦 真绪
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.77,0:20:39.56,Default,,0,0,0,,真的很合身
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.94,0:20:40.79,Default,,0,0,0,,是吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.17,0:20:45.09,Default,,0,0,0,,第一次见真绪穿这种衣服呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.75,0:20:49.15,Default,,0,0,0,,真绪不想成为英雄了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.07,0:20:51.91,Default,,0,0,0,,我已经放弃成为英雄了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.14,0:20:56.70,Default,,0,0,0,,为 为什么？ 真绪你不是非常想成为英雄的吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.09,0:20:59.74,Default,,0,0,0,,不是说过想成为长枪骑士这样的人吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.09,0:20:59.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs30\pos(657.2,665)}Knight Lancer
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.06,0:21:01.50,Default,,0,0,0,,这就是为了长枪骑士
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.06,0:21:01.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs30\pos(723.2,665)}Knight Lancer
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.56,0:21:07.06,Default,,0,0,0,,今后我要成为与他相称的女士
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.28,0:21:12.29,Default,,0,0,0,,长枪骑士一直称我为女士
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.28,0:21:12.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs30\pos(521.2,665)}Knight Lancer
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.88,0:21:15.72,Default,,0,0,0,,而我不能成为他口中的名副其实的女士的话
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.06,0:21:18.36,Default,,0,0,0,,可就要给长枪骑士蒙羞了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.06,0:21:18.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs30\pos(657.2,665)}Knight Lancer
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.93,0:21:22.46,Default,,0,0,0,,所以我才要做一个配得上长枪骑士的女士
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.93,0:21:22.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs30\pos(773.2,665)}Knight Lancer
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.95,0:21:26.37,Default,,0,0,0,,然后…成为长枪骑士的妻子
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.95,0:21:26.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs30\pos(671.2,665)}Knight Lancer
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.74,0:21:28.23,Default,,0,0,0,,诶？！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.89,0:21:32.33,Default,,0,0,0,,长枪骑士向我求婚了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.89,0:21:32.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs30\pos(557.2,665)}Knight Lancer
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.55,0:21:36.36,Default,,0,0,0,,他许下了一生守护着我的诺言
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.64,0:21:41.24,Default,,0,0,0,,那这也就是要和我白头偕老的意思了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.48,0:21:43.36,Default,,0,0,0,,不 不 应该还没到那地步…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.89,0:21:46.30,Default,,0,0,0,,骑士绝不能口出虚言
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.39,0:21:47.63,Default,,0,0,0,,依 依子小姐…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.75,0:21:49.77,Default,,0,0,0,,这是怎么回事 叶太郎大人！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.77,0:21:50.38,Default,,0,0,0,,不…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.38,0:21:53.72,Default,,0,0,0,,可不能随便就和真绪说结婚这种话
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.77,0:21:56.85,Default,,0,0,0,,人家才6岁啊 而且…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.05,0:22:00.47,Default,,0,0,0,,莫 莫非叶太郎大人其实是萝莉控？！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.47,0:22:03.44,Default,,0,0,0,,想娶我为妻的可是长枪骑士哦
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.47,0:22:03.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs30\pos(755.2,665)}Knight Lancer
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.08,0:22:05.92,Default,,0,0,0,,啊 那 那个啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.92,0:22:07.40,Default,,0,0,0,,爱丽丝你真奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.61,0:22:09.34,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯 是的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.95,0:23:51.83,Default,,0,0,0,,老大好
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.83,0:23:53.18,Default,,0,0,0,,打扰了 白姬老大
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.52,0:23:54.84,Default,,0,0,0,,老大 白姬你？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.84,0:23:58.07,Default,,0,0,0,,白姬可是君临着学园的恐怖支配者
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.07,0:24:00.04,Default,,0,0,0,,无法想象熊孩子啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.04,0:24:00.88,Default,,0,0,0,,真烦人
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.48,0:24:05.12,Default,,0,0,0,,白姬的铁蹄正在嘶吼
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.12,0:24:06.89,Default,,0,0,0,,别让你那东西嘶吼啊喂
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.89,0:24:09.28,Default,,0,0,0,,这种恶女的形象才是白姬魅力所在嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.28,0:24:11.06,Default,,0,0,0,,与其说是恶女 不如说只是熊孩子罢了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.06,0:24:15.13,Default,,0,0,0,,好了 那下一集 新来了个迷之转学生和不是转学生的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.13,0:24:17.44,Default,,0,0,0,,新来的得好好教训教训才对
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.44,0:24:19.49,Default,,0,0,0,,所以说别做坏事啊
